## 🎫 ParkingTicket

### Attributes
| Attribute | Type | Description |
|-----------|------|-------------|
| ticket_id | int | Unique identifier |
| vehicle | Vehicle | Parked vehicle |
| spot | ParkingSpot | Assigned spot |
| entry_time | datetime | When vehicle entered |
| exit_time | datetime | When vehicle exited (None until exit) |

### Methods
| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `get_duration_hours()` | Calculate parking duration |

### Implementation
```python
class ParkingTicket:
    def __init__(self, ticket_id, vehicle, spot):
        self.ticket_id = ticket_id
        self.vehicle = vehicle
        self.spot = spot
        self.entry_time = datetime.now()
        self.exit_time = None
    
    def get_duration_hours(self) -> float:
        end = self.exit_time or datetime.now()
        duration = end - self.entry_time
        return duration.total_seconds() / 3600
```

